<Project Sdk="Microsoft.NET.Sdk">

  <PropertyGroup>
    <TargetFramework>netstandard2.0</TargetFramework>
    <RootNamespace>NKristek.Smaragd</RootNamespace>
    <AssemblyName>NKristek.Smaragd</AssemblyName>
    <Version>4.0</Version>
    <Description>Base classes for implementing an C# .NET application using the MVVM architecture</Description>
    <Company>nkristek</Company>
    <Authors>nkristek</Authors>
    <Product>Smaragd</Product>
    <PackageId>NKristek.Smaragd</PackageId>
    <Copyright>Copyright Â©  2018 Niclas Kristek</Copyright>
    <PackageLicenseExpression>MIT</PackageLicenseExpression>
    <PackageProjectUrl>https://github.com/nkristek/Smaragd</PackageProjectUrl>
    <RepositoryUrl>https://github.com/nkristek/Smaragd.git</RepositoryUrl>
    <GeneratePackageOnBuild>true</GeneratePackageOnBuild>
    <RepositoryType>git</RepositoryType>
    <PackageTags></PackageTags>
    <PackageReleaseNotes>This release includes improved XML documentation, more interfaces and more:
- adjust visibility of methods and make more methods virtual
- ViewModelCommand and AsyncViewModelCommand now has a Name property which defaults to the name of its type including its namespace
- remove BindableCommand and integrate logic in ViewModelCommand
- abstract method ViewModelCommand.DoExecute is now called Execute
- remove AsyncBindableCommand and integrate logic in AsyncViewModelCommand
- abstract method AsyncViewModelCommand.DoExecute is now called ExecuteAsync
- throw ArgumentNullExceptions for parameters which should not be null
- rename BindableBase to Bindable
- rename ComputedBindableBase to ComputedBindable
- ComputedBindable now introduces a virtual RaisePropertyChanged method with all indirect notified propertyNames as a second argument
- ViewModel now has a Commands property of type Dictionary&lt;string, ICommand&gt;. The key will be its name, the value the command itself. Commands should be added to this Dictionary for the CanExecuteSourceAttribute to work
- Bindable now implements INotifyPropertyChanging in addition to INotifyPropertyChanged

New interfaces:
- INamedCommand: Defines a Name property which uniquely identifies the command
- IRaiseErrorsChanged: Provides methods for raising events on the ErrorsChanged event handler.
- IRaisePropertyChanged: Provides methods for raising events on the PropertyChanged event handler.
- IDialogModel: Defines a viewmodel to use in a dialog
- ITreeViewModel: Defines a viewmodel to use in a tree view
- IValidatingViewModel: Defines a viewmodel which performs validation
- IViewModel: Defines a viewmodel</PackageReleaseNotes>
    <NeutralLanguage>en</NeutralLanguage>
    <AssemblyVersion>4.0.0.0</AssemblyVersion>
    <FileVersion>4.0.0.0</FileVersion>
  </PropertyGroup>

  <PropertyGroup Condition="'$(Configuration)|$(Platform)'=='Release|AnyCPU'">
    <LangVersion>latest</LangVersion>
    <DocumentationFile>bin\Release\netstandard2.0\NKristek.Smaragd.xml</DocumentationFile>
  </PropertyGroup>

</Project>
